Key Match Events: Michael Busch hit a home run that cleared the short fence in the left-field corner, and Cody Bellinger hit a two-run homer as part of a three-RBI night.
Post-Match Reflections: Cody Bellinger reflected on the game, saying that Michael Busch can 'kind of lock it in when there's extra things going on.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Cubs' 10-4 win was powered by former Dodgers Michael Busch and Cody Bellinger.
